      "metadata": {
        "id": "35f33843"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 13. Pré-processamento"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 20,
      "id": "9f345a39",
      "metadata": {
        "execution": {
          "iopub.execute_input": "2026-07-15T23:21:11.350001Z",
          "iopub.status.busy": "2026-07-15T23:21:11.349854Z",
          "iopub.status.idle": "2026-07-15T23:21:11.353441Z",
          "shell.execute_reply": "2026-07-15T23:21:11.352543Z"
        },
        "id": "9f345a39"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "numeric_transformer = Pipeline([\n",
        "    ('imputer', SimpleImputer(strategy='median')),\n",
        "    ('scaler', StandardScaler())\n",
        "])\n",
        "\n",
        "categorical_transformer = Pipeline([\n",
        "    ('imputer', SimpleImputer(strategy='constant', fill_value='Missing')),\n",
        "    ('onehot', OneHotEncoder(handle_unknown='ignore', sparse_output=False))\n",
        "])\n",
        "\n",
        "preprocessor = ColumnTransformer([\n",
        "    ('num', numeric_transformer, numeric_features),\n",
        "    ('cat', categorical_transformer, categorical_features)\n",
        "])"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "6b0b3237",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "6b0b3237"
      },
      "source": [
        "- `SimpleImputer`: preenche nulos;\n",
        "- mediana: robusta a extremos;\n",
        "- `StandardScaler`: média 0 e desvio 1;\n",
        "- `OneHotEncoder`: transforma categorias em colunas 0/1;\n",
        "- `handle_unknown='ignore'`: aceita categorias novas;\n",
        "- `ColumnTransformer`: aplica tratamentos por tipo."
      ]
    },
